{"tid":1697764,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"若這件事沒發生 比爾蓋茲：Windows Mobile能成為市場主流","createTime":"2019-11-07T04:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:18:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"39f2ff85f3aad82fb17fc252e5b25846387ffb8c","tid":1697764,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2970080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2970080&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=cf10fe1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2970080&h=effb2a08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2970080</a><br />\n<br />\n儘管微軟（Microsoft）目前在電腦作業系統佔據全球市場主導地位，但在手機作業系統方面完全沒有任何機會。微軟創辦人比爾蓋茲（Bill Gates）6日表示，要不是美國司法部在1998年對微軟發起反壟斷調查，微軟的手機作業系統Windows Mobile現在可能早已在全球佔據主導地位。<br />\n《CNBC》報導，比爾蓋茲6日在紐約參加《紐約時報》舉辦的DealBook大會時表示，1998年美國司法部對微軟發起的反壟斷訴訟，對微軟很不利，「我們原本會更專注於開發手機作業系統。因此，如果沒有當年的反壟斷案，現在消費者就不會使用安卓系統了，而是使用Windows Mobile」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比爾蓋茲說：「我們就差點就成功了。那個時候我的注意力受到了干擾，而這種干擾導致我把事情搞砸了。」<br />\n報導分析，比爾蓋茲的這番言論表明，針對當今其他大型科技公司所發起的反壟斷案件，可能會給這些企業造成負面影響。目前臉書、Alphabet、蘋果、亞馬遜都面臨反壟斷調查的相關危機。<br />\n今年早些時候，比爾蓋茲曾表示，他在微軟犯下的最大錯誤，就是沒有讓Windows成為世界主流的手機作業系統。蓋茨6日還表示，若不是因為美國政府從1998年開始對微軟發起的反壟斷調查，他也不會這麼早就退休。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/07/UBmHcE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F07%2FUBmHcE.png&h=422e47e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58548aedf8378cc00dd22d36fdb3af8006b12d00","tid":1697764,"uid":12628,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"比你垃圾不知進取window mobile 統治到世界，科技就真係已死喇"},{"pid":"da68981556106bf9fc5be8c5beecc615b44c965a","tid":1697764,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"Windows Mobile 6.5 果個年代其實仲用WinCE Kernel 先搞到咁衰<br />\n如果當年Skip 咗WP7, 直上WP8 個NT Kernel 真係未必無得鬥<br />\n當年WM6.5 生態都幾好"},{"pid":"b41e68cccf816f0cf18d010d7bcf6642169dc58a","tid":1697764,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da68981556106bf9fc5be8c5beecc615b44c965a","tid":1697764,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"Windows Mobile 6.5 果個年代其實仲用WinCE Kernel 先搞到咁衰<br />\n如果當年Skip 咗WP7, 直上WP8 個NT Kernel 真係未必無得鬥<br />\n當年WM6.5 生態都幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾中嘅垃圾Window mobile 成功到，連比佢無咁垃圾嘅window phone 都無呀。"},{"pid":"5e65e76d83f2ff1a41233fff3b9655e6ba56d1a1","tid":1697764,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦。佢d Mobile OS真心垃圾到爆。"},{"pid":"199a793c4e90e8eed94a59710546224e8f707fae","tid":1697764,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"**眾籌***<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先45%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=40Eeu%2FLL